Symbol.Script_3D:
! Economizer
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, A/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -A/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
CYLIND ZZYZX, A/2
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
RESOL res CUTPOLYA 2, 2, 0, 0, 0, 979, A/2, 360, 4079
IF ConStatus_3 THEN ! --- UPPER SIDE CONNECTION --- ! ADDz ConPosZ_3 ROTx 90 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, A/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_3/2+ConWallThickness_3, 360, 4001 DEL 2 ENDIF
IF ConStatus_4 THEN ! --- UPPER SIDE CONNECTION --- ! ADDz ConPosZ_4 ROTx 90 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, A/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_4/2+ConWallThickness_4, 360, 4001 DEL 2 ENDIF CUTEND
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 1, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 14, ConEdgeVisible_3 = 0, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConPosZ_4=ConPosZ_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConEdit_4 = 14, ConEdgeVisible_4 = 0 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Economizer
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, A/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -A/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT 0, 0, 901, A/2, 360, 4001
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
IF ConStatus_3 THEN ! --- LOWER SIDE CONNECTION --- ! hCW3 = ConWidth_3/2+ConWallThickness_3
PUT 0, -A/2, 1, 1, 0, 801, hCW3, -SQR((A/2)^2-(hCW3)^2), 1001, hCW3, -A/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT 0, -A/2, 1, -1, 0, 801, -hCW3, -SQR((A/2)^2-(hCW3)^2), 1001, -hCW3, -A/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF
IF ConStatus_4 THEN ! --- UPPER SIDE CONNECTION --- ! hCW4 = ConWidth_4/2+ConWallThickness_4
PUT 0, -A/2, 1, 1, 0, 801, hCW4, -SQR((A/2)^2-(hCW4)^2), 1001, hCW4, -A/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT 0, -A/2, 1, -1, 0, 801, -hCW4, -SQR((A/2)^2-(hCW4)^2), 1001, -hCW4, -A/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 0, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 0, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_3 = 0, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConEdit_4 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_4 = 0 DEL 1
END
